name: Pinder - Are You Coming With Me? (Feat Dyce Dylli)

attributes.trait_type: Are You Coming With Me? (Feat Dyce Dylli)

lyrics.text:
Downtrodden 
Cold hearted 
Cold blooded 
The game jade you
Niggas hate you for getting money 
I need something, I went off, I was hungry, I need quickly, I move swiftly, we went hunting 
You hesitate in war you dead, 
Why I feel like most the battles in my head
Real sticky, can’t shake it, can’t break it, can’t make it 
You start to force it, dark forces, not fortune 

I need 50, 2 50’s, that’s one hundred, one homie he start gunning, it start running
Dark summers, fools gather for hood summits and shared traumas, shared notes and baby momma

Had the lint inside my pocket, playing with the texture, I was sitting cross the street from the dealer with the Lexus 
I had options, I made choices, I was dealing with the voices
If I can make it through then I rejoice it 

Look we ain’t goin up for nothing 
We needin for something 
Paths unlock take a risk and it’s jumpin
Make one wrong move slip fall and you plummet 
No butterflies in the stomach you either comin or not

If I go down, are you with? 
If I go down you come with? 
If I go down for the risk now my brother are you coming with? 

Responsibilities for my abilities 
I make something happen, out of nothing often
All the pressure on me, bring desperation on me
Heater on me, paranoia, I don’t trust the homies 
See experience, repetitive, I done heard and I said the shit, Seen the shit in nightmares past, I confronted it 
Really think that I wanted it, chased it maybe I caught it. Might not be the luck that you think, maybe I got it 

Could turn to the curse of the ego to hurt people 
Could start out the purest intentions still turn evil 
How much power till you hit limits of that corruption 
The opposite of what they expect, I be disrupting 

I didn’t listen when they said I should stop I kept it bussin 
We ain’t even call resilient, We was just hustling 
Just to get little money to get up again, and draw it up again, and pick it up again 

Look we ain’t goin up for nothing 
We needin for something 
Paths unlock take a risk and it’s jumpin
Make one wrong move slip fall and you plummet 
No butterflies in the stomach you either comin or not

God damn 
Are you coming with me?
